Title: Bling Jewelry AYLLU Warm Emrbace 925 Silver Small Brooch Pin
Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Love. Luck. Unity. Represent your values with a beautiful piece from our AYLLU collection. AYLLU is the Quechua word for community. To create this collection, Elena Castaneda, founder of Bling Jewelry, drew inspiration from her Peruvian-born father. When his childhood friends immigrated to America, they were welcomed with an embrace and exclamation of "Ayllu!" to remind them that their community extended from their shared past into their shared future in a new land. Three well known symbols intertwine to make up the AYLLU: hearts for love, an infinity entwined forever and a clover for good fortune. Just like a community with different minds and ideas, they come together to form one meaning - the symbol of AYLLU. Gift this petite electrocoated sterling silver brooch pin to yourself or someone special in your own community. You will be making a difference in the life of someone that you know, as well as others that you don't know. Bling Jewelry donates 20% of the proceeds from our AYLLU collection to Pencils of Promise -- a nonprofit organization that builds schools and education programs for children around the globe. Wear your ring with pride and start a conversation about what community means to you. Go beyond borders and beyond languages, celebrate differences and live your life with AYLLU in mind. - AYLLU Symbol Small Brooch Pin - Can Be Worn As a Hat or Lapel Pin - Material: .925 Sterling Silver, Electrocoating - Measure: 1 inch L x 1 inch W - Weight: 2.4 Grams Bling Jewelry AYLLU Warm Emrbace 925 Silver Small Brooch Pin
